name: ToxicologicalEmergency
title: Toxicological Emergency
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent a diagnosis of a toxicological emergency.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with a diagnosis of a toxicological emergency, including poisoning and adverse or toxic effects of various agents or substances.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts related to underdosing.)
